Package org.typemeta.funcj.json.model

This package contains data structures that model JSON data.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonAlg<T>
    An object algebra interface for JSON values.
    JsonAlg.Query<T>
    A query is a an object algebra operation that traverses the JsValue, and computes an aggregate value.
    JsonAlg.Transform<T>
    A transform is a an object algebra operation that traverses the JsValue, and constructs another structure.
    JsValue
    Common interface for classes that represent JSON values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JSAPI  
    JsArray
    Models a JSON array.
    JsNumber
    Models a JSON number value.
    JsObject
    Models a JSON object.
    JsObject.Field  
    JsonAlg.Query.Base<T>  
    JsonAlg.Transform.Base<T>  
    JsString
    Models a JSON string.
    Utils  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JsBool
    Models JSON true and false values.
    JsNull
    Models a JSON null value.
